    <div class="faq-a" id="chatgpt-search"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>ChatGPT uses Bing's index to find and cite web sources. A study found that 71% of pages cited by ChatGPT use schema markup. ChatGPT favors pages with clear authorship signals (Person schema), publication dates, and organizational identity.</p></div></div>
