    <div class="faq-a" id="claude-and-grok"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Claude (Anthropic) and Grok (xAI) both introduced web search capabilities. Both prefer authoritative, well-annotated content. Our guides on <a href="/blog/claude-search-optimization/">Claude search optimization</a> and <a href="/blog/grok-search-seo/">Grok search SEO</a> cover platform-specific tactics.</p></div></div>
